          I live in <b>Madison, Wisconsin</b>. Also known as: <i style="color: #0095ff; font-weight: bold">cold</i>. But lucky for me (and my hardware), I prefer a cold Winter over a hot
          Summer. Madison has been a great city as a young developer. It has a lot of diversity, activities, and a suprisingly large
